docs.snippet: The R. M. steamship Persia, from Liverpool on the 4th inst., with three days' later news from Europe, is now fully due at this port. There were no signs of her at Sandy Hook at 12 o'clock last night.

docs.lead_paragraph: NEW STEAMBOAT FOR THE TEHUANTEPEC ROUTE.--A new non steamboat, to be called the Suchul, was yesterday launched from the ship-yard fool of Houston street, East River, for the Louisania Tehuantepee Company. She has been constructed by BOARDMAN, HILBROOK CO, of the Neptune Iron Works, in an incredibly short time, forty two working days only having been employed in doing the work.
